<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.6">
<l>nōkki nōkki yuṉṉaik kāṇpāṉ yāṉeṉa tāviyuḷḷē</l>
<l>nākku nīḷvaṉ ñāṉa millai nāṭōṟu meṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>vākkai yuḷḷu māvi yuḷḷu mallapu ṟattiṉuḷḷum</l>
<l>nīkka miṉṟi yeṅku niṉṟāy niṉṉai yaṟintaṟintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Looking [and] looking I will see you inside my soul,</l>
<l>– There is no long, strong knowledge of the tongue. –,</l>
<l>knowing [and] knowing you, you who stand always without leaving</l>
<l>in my body, soul and in the outside which is neither, every day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
